🐻 Build-A-Bear Hackathon | Main Track
Ranger is running a 4-week online hackathon to build and deploy vault strategies on Solana — giving participants a chance to showcase their edge and fast-track their way to running a live product with real AUM behind it.

Who it's for: Traders and developers who have a yield or trading strategy they want to experiment with and scale. Solo or team.

What you can build: Production-ready vault strategies. Basis trades, delta-neutral, RWA, AI-driven, or anything novel.

Why: Winning strategies get seeded with real TVL (up to $1M on this track) and deployed on-chain via Ranger Earn. Vault managers earn ongoing performance fees post-hackathon.

All teams are eligible for the Main Track. If you want to compete for the Drift Side Track prizes as well, submit separately on the Drift Side Track page.

🏆 Main Track Prizes
1st Place — Up to $500,000 in vault seeding

2nd Place — Up to $300,000 in vault seeding

3rd Place — Up to $200,000 in vault seeding

