✅ Prize Eligibility Requirements
Review carefully before building. Strategies that don't meet these requirements will not be eligible for seeding prizes regardless of competition performance.

Minimum APY: 10%

Vault Base Asset: USDC

Tenor: 3-month lock, rolling — reassessed every 3 months

Disqualifying yield sources:

Ponzi-like yield-bearing stables — circular yield dependencies (e.g. Vault A exposes to YBS X, Y, Z where X depends on Y, Y depends on Z, Z depends on X). Can cause death spirals.

Junior tranche / insurance pool designs — e.g. RLP, jrUSDe. Carry principal loss risk.

DEX LP vaults — e.g. JLP, HLP, LLP. Carry impermanent loss / principal loss risk.

High-leverage looping — health rate below 1.05 on assets whose price is not hardcoded in the oracle.

Prize Disclaimer

Vault seeding amounts are indicative and awarded at Presto Labs' discretion based on strategy quality and seeding requirements.

